cs.LG, cs.GT, cs.IT, cs.DS, cs.CC

The paper discusses online learning algorithms and their applications in optimization and game theory. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also discusses matrix games, which falls under cs.GT (Game Theory). The paper also mentions partial information, which is related to cs.IT (Information Theory). The paper also discusses convex programming, which falls under cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.CC (Computational Complexity).
